---
title: One-Pot Yellow Curry Chicken Noodle Soup with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: Dig into our flavour-packed yellow curry soup, both heartwarming and easy to prepare. The spice-infused broth is rich in flavour and packed with tender pan-fried chicken and tossed veggies all bundled together with udon noodles. We’re sure you’ll come back for more!
